{"tid":573565,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔是如何練成-論連登及會員生態","createTime":"2018-02-26T14:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T16:20:12.000Z","uid":68626,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aa38b9716a3c0604f4debf63f557dfa14483f31a","tid":573565,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"大家好 我係會員 詭辯家<br />\n可能大家唔識我 但係唔緊要<br />\n我今日係想同大家分享下 我平時發文 同上連登個陣係諗緊咩<br />\n自我上連登以來 都算係活躍會員 唔多唔少都有少少感觸<br />\n其實我係現實係一個好有正義感同有愛心既人<br />\n我係出每個POST之前 都係有一個既定立場 傾向收正評定負評<br />\n例如 覺唔覺檢舉free rider好撚on9? 我係傾向想收負評 結果就如我所願<br />\n但係 覺唔覺班nursing撚好撚扮野? 就收左好多正評 但其實我係支持nursing撚 收左正評其實我係好唔開心<br />\n可能有好多壇友話我平時引戰 刷存在感等等<br />\n我諗各位可能有少少誤會 論壇本身就係拎黎討論既地方 引戰有咩問題? 我應該話引戰先係論壇既本質<br />\n至於刷存在感 原來會有人覺得持某d意見會同刷存在感掛勾 真係幾奇怪 事實上我不知幾想連登有個匿名出post系統<br />\n其實連登仔係一群羊 而且佢地往往感情用事 對於發文者既語氣 去決定對個樣野既評價<br />\n我舉兩個post做例子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/556948/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/556948/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/556095/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/556095/page/1</a><br />\n其實分別只係一個樓主好聲氣少少 一個樓主串少少 結果就完全唔同<br />\n成班就突然覺得另一個樓主講得好岩 比負評班友就突然人格分裂/由地球上消失<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/571647/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/571647/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/572756/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/572756/page/1</a><br />\n同一例子 成班友突然精神分裂覺得幾千萬美金值錢過人脈 咁當初比負評班友去左邊?<br />\n連登仔另一個特質就係 嚴人寬己<br />\n例如我出任何一個POST笑鳩某類人 成班就會出黎護航 攻擊樓主等等<br />\n但係當自己係到種族歧視個陣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/571702/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/571702/page/1</a> 就一副我笑鳩人你吹咩既心態<br />\n可能有人想覆咩上連登勿認真 認真你就輸了<br />\n依加好多中學雞上連登 如果下一代個個都係咁樣 我真係唔知講咩好 共勉之"},{"pid":"1f76f9541e59d38f3001e08ffd537599f2bc48ac","tid":573565,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"金鐘M記.jpg"},{"pid":"753d73e0ff277c54a4d74b436f98afa4c2553d48","tid":573565,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:22:11.000Z","msg":"樓主好撚垃圾 成日敗走<br />\n係高登已經係過街老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日搵野同人嘈 比人圍就開新post搵其他野嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要講典型連登仔 樓主當之無愧"},{"pid":"87bf06751b8f41629038ee83c2335d05569fe7bb","tid":573565,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T15:26:00.000Z","msg":"Too long didn't read <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過每次屌連登囝嘅post都呃到大量正皮<br />\n<br />\n睇吓今次係咪都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0768847c35129d52a1836ac2455dee5fcb42b22","tid":573565,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T16:12:14.000Z","msg":"只想講佢哋好撚羊群 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974b2c16666957bc3e977b95a8f5e6c835de8edf","tid":573565,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T16:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/001926_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F001926_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=283e89ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n狂野<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/001940_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F001940_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=45abf60e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nwow<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/001952_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload